<p>Based on this conceptual relation between climate change and vulnerability, we designed an econometric strategy to estimate the impact. The calculation of the probability of being in a condition of undernourishment implies information about the probability distribution function of caloric consumption of each household. In its projections of undernourishment, FAO utilizes a lognormal distribution for caloric consumption [
 <xref rid="pone.0222483.ref023" ref-type="bibr">23</xref>], which has also been empirically validated, for example [
 <xref rid="pone.0222483.ref024" ref-type="bibr">24</xref>]. Assuming the said distribution of caloric consumption, the vulnerability of each household is given by: 
